<item>
            <title>[LU-4021] Volatile files should be accessible on all clients</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4021</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Any clients should be able to open_by_fid a volatile file. This is a requirement for copy tools capable of parallel restore, like Grau Data.&lt;br/&gt;
Add it to 2.5 blockers as per my discussion with Andreas today.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="21185">LU-4021</key>
            <summary>Volatile files should be accessible on all clients</summary>
